<section class="section s7-faq">
  <div class="container--narrow">

    <h2 class="s7-faq__heading">Frequently asked questions</h2>

    <div class="s7-faq__list">

      <details class="s7-faq__item">
        <summary class="s7-faq__question">What is Glutathione and why is it good for my skin?</summary>
        <div class="s7-faq__answer">
          <p>Glutathione is a powerful antioxidant naturally produced by your body. It plays a key role in neutralizing free radicals, reducing oxidative stress, and inhibiting melanin production, which helps brighten the skin and reduce hyperpigmentation. As we age, glutathione levels decline, making IV supplementation an effective way to restore this beauty-essential compound at therapeutic levels.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="s7-faq__item">
        <summary class="s7-faq__question">How is this IV drip better than topical creams or serums?</summary>
        <div class="s7-faq__answer">
          <p>Topical skincare products must penetrate multiple layers of skin to reach the dermis where collagen and cellular activity occur, and most active ingredients are significantly diluted in this process. IV delivery bypasses the digestive and skin barrier entirely, delivering nutrients directly into your bloodstream for near-100% bioavailability. This means your cells receive far higher concentrations of active ingredients than any topical product can provide.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="s7-faq__item">
        <summary class="s7-faq__question">How long does it take to see results for my skin, hair, and nails?</summary>
        <div class="s7-faq__answer">
          <p>Many clients notice improved skin luminosity and energy within 24 to 48 hours of their first session. Visible improvements in skin texture, hair shine, and nail strength typically develop over 2 to 4 weeks as your body responds to the increased nutrient availability. For optimal results, we recommend a series of treatments spaced 2 to 4 weeks apart.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="s7-faq__item">
        <summary class="s7-faq__question">How often should I get a Beauty IV drip to maintain results?</summary>
        <div class="s7-faq__answer">
          <p>For initial results, we typically recommend a series of 3 to 4 sessions spaced 2 to 4 weeks apart. For maintenance, monthly or bi-monthly sessions help sustain and build upon your results over time. Your provider will recommend a personalized schedule based on your goals and response to treatment.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="s7-faq__item">
        <summary class="s7-faq__question">Who is a good candidate for a Beauty IV Drip?</summary>
        <div class="s7-faq__answer">
          <p>Our Anti-Aging &amp; Beauty IV is suitable for most healthy adults looking to improve skin radiance, reduce signs of aging, or strengthen hair and nails. We conduct a brief health screening before treatment to ensure it is appropriate for you. Those who are pregnant, breastfeeding, or have certain medical conditions may not be candidates. Schedule a consultation to discuss whether this treatment is right for you.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s7-faq__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .s7-faq__list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .s7-faq__item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .s7-faq__item[open] .s7-faq__question {
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
  }

  .s7-faq__question {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: var(--space-sm) 0;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    line-height: 1.5;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .s7-faq__question::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .s7-faq__question::after {
    content: '+';
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-text);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .s7-faq__item[open] .s7-faq__question::after {
    content: '\2212';
  }

  .s7-faq__answer {
    padding: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
  }

  .s7-faq__answer p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
